                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Lapor Diri Secara Atas Talian.', 'Menghubungi Jabatan Sumber Manusia melalui platform digital untuk pengesahan kehadiran.', 'Menghantar borang-borang keperluan syarikat dan politeknik.'], 'activities_en' => ['Online check-in.', 'Contacted Human Resources Department through digital platform for attendance verification.', 'Submitted required company and polytechnic forms.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Orientasi Kendiri dan Pemahaman Latar Belakang Syarikat.', 'Meneliti senarai perkhidmatan atau produk yang ditawarkan oleh syarikat.', 'Mengenalpasti fungsi setiap jabatan.', 'Menyediakan persiapan dokumen fizikal untuk sesi lapor diri pada pejabat hari berikutnya.'], 'activities_en' => ['Self-orientation and understanding company background.', 'Reviewed the list of services or products offered by the company.', 'Identified the function of each department.', 'Prepared physical documents for office check-in the following day.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Lapor Diri Fizikal dan Sesi Orientasi Jabatan.', 'Melapor diri kepada penyelia dan bahagian Sumber Manusia (HR).', 'Sesi suai kenal bersama ahli pasukan dan melihat kawasan sekitar pejabat.', 'Menerima taklimat mengenai peraturan syarikat dan tugasan yang bakal diberikan.', 'Mengemas kini dan menyediakan ruang kerja/meja kerja.'], 'activities_en' => ['Physical check-in and department orientation session.', 'Reported to supervisor and Human Resources (HR) department.', 'Ice-breaking session with team members and toured office surroundings.', 'Received briefing on company regulations and upcoming tasks.', 'Set up and prepared workspace/desk.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Penyediaan Dokumentasi Manual Pengguna bagi Sistem mySafe (Bahagian Fungsi Butang).', 'Meneliti dan mengenalpasti fungsi setiap butang yang terdapat dalam Sistem mySafe.', 'Menyusun maklumat fungsi butang ke dalam bentuk jadual bagi memudahkan pemahaman pengguna.', 'Mendokumentasikan fungsi butang utama seperti butang \'Menu\' untuk navigasi sistem.', 'Memastikan ikon yang digunakan dalam dokumentasi sepadan dengan ikon sebenar dalam sistem.'], 'activities_en' => ['Prepared User Manual Documentation for mySafe System (Button Functions Section).', 'Studied and identified the function of each button in the mySafe System.', 'Organised button function information into table format for easier user understanding.', 'Documented main button functions such as the \'Menu\' button for system navigation.', 'Ensured icons used in documentation matched actual icons in the system.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Penyediaan Dokumentasi Modul Pentadbiran bagi Sistem mySafe.', 'Meneliti fungsi Modul Pentadbiran merangkumi Pengurusan Data Induk dan Tetapan Sistem.', 'Melengkapkan manual bagi sub-modul utama bermula dari Tempat, Syarikat, Pengguna sampai ke CMS.'], 'activities_en' => ['Prepared Administration Module Documentation for mySafe System.', 'Studied the Administration Module functions covering Master Data Management and System Settings.', 'Completed manual for main sub-modules from Location, Company, User to CMS.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Aktiviti minggu ini melibatkan proses lapor diri secara atas talian dan fizikal serta sesi orientasi sistem mySafe. Tugasan utama adalah menyediakan Manual Pengguna yang merangkumi dokumentasi fungsi butang dan Modul Pentadbiran. Saya berjaya memahami aliran kerja teknikal sistem mySafe serta mempelajari cara penulisan dokumentasi yang ringkas dan mudah difahami. Pengalaman menguruskan sub-modul secara sistematik telah meningkatkan kemahiran teknikal saya dalam memahami struktur data sistem maklumat dan cara berkomunikasi secara profesional di pejabat. Latihan ini meningkatkan keyakinan saya dalam mengendalikan dokumentasi sistem dan memupuk sifat teliti bagi mengelakkan ralat maklumat. Secara keseluruhan, saya mendapat gambaran mengenai tugas sokongan IT dan kepentingan pengurusan data yang teratur dalam sesebuah organisasi.', 'reflection_en' => 'This week\'s activities involved the process of online and physical check-in as well as mySafe system orientation sessions. The main task was to prepare a User Manual covering button function documentation and the Administration Module. I managed to understand the technical workflow of the mySafe system and learned how to write concise and easy-to-understand documentation. The experience of managing sub-modules systematically has enhanced my technical skills in understanding information system data structures and communicating professionally in the office. This training increased my confidence in handling system documentation and cultivated meticulousness to avoid information errors. Overall, I gained an overview of IT support tasks and the importance of organised data management in an organisation.'],
            ['title_ms' => 'MINGGU 2', 'title_en' => 'WEEK 2', 'start_date' => '2026-01-19', 'end_date' => '2026-01-23', 'days' => [
                ['day_ms' => 'Isnin', 'day_en' => 'Monday', 'activities_ms' => ['Menyambung penyediaan Manual Pengguna bagi Sistem mySafe.', 'Fokus kepada sub-modul Tetapan Sistem sehingga bahagian Meja Bantuan (Helpdesk).', 'Melengkapkan separuh daripada panduan konfigurasi untuk rujukan pengguna.'], 'activities_en' => ['Continued preparing User Manual for mySafe System.', 'Focused on System Settings sub-module up to Helpdesk section.', 'Completed half of the configuration guide for user reference.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Selasa', 'day_en' => 'Tuesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Melengkapkan baki dokumentasi Manual Pengguna bagi sub-modul Meja Bantuan.', 'Menyusun keseluruhan manual mengikut turutan kedudukan butang dalam sistem.', 'Melakukan semakan akhir bagi memastikan setiap fungsi didokumentasikan dengan tepat.'], 'activities_en' => ['Completed remaining User Manual documentation for Helpdesk sub-module.', 'Organised entire manual following button placement order in the system.', 'Performed final review to ensure every function was documented accurately.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Rabu', 'day_en' => 'Wednesday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Kecemasan (Emergency Leave).'], 'activities_en' => ['Emergency Leave.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Khamis', 'day_en' => 'Thursday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Kecemasan (Emergency Leave).'], 'activities_en' => ['Emergency Leave.']],
                ['day_ms' => 'Jumaat', 'day_en' => 'Friday', 'activities_ms' => ['Cuti Kecemasan (Emergency Leave).'], 'activities_en' => ['Emergency Leave.']],
            ], 'reflection_ms' => 'Aktiviti minggu kedua memfokuskan kepada penyambungan baki Manual Pengguna bagi modul Tetapan Sistem sehingga Log Sistem. Walau bagaimanapun, penglibatan kerja hanya dilakukan selama dua hari kerana saya telah mengambil cuti kecemasan bagi baki tiga hari yang lain. Masa yang ada digunakan untuk memastikan draf dokumentasi modul akhir disiapkan sebelum cuti bermula. Saya mendapat pendedahan mengenai pengurusan masa dan tanggungjawab kerja apabila perlu menyiapkan tugasan penting sebelum mengambil cuti. Selain itu, saya mempelajari fungsi teknikal di bawah modul Meja Bantuan seperti pengurusan status kerja. Latihan minggu ini memberi impak terhadap kepentingan komunikasi yang jelas bersama penyelia ketika memohon cuti kecemasan bagi memastikan kelancaran operasi pejabat. Saya juga memahami aliran sokongan teknikal sistem dan merasa lebih bertanggungjawab dalam menguruskan tugasan dokumentasi yang diberikan walaupun dalam kekangan waktu yang singkat.', 'reflection_en' => 'Week two activities focused on continuing the remaining User Manual for the System Settings module up to System Log. However, work involvement was only for two days as I took emergency leave for the remaining three days. The available time was used to ensure the final module documentation draft was completed before the leave began. I gained exposure on time management and work responsibility when needing to complete important tasks before taking leave. Additionally, I learned technical functions under the Helpdesk module such as work status management. This week\'s training highlighted the importance of clear communication with supervisors when applying for emergency leave to ensure smooth office operations. I also understood the system technical support workflow and felt more responsible in managing documentation tasks given despite the short time constraint.'],
